snippet.title: Oorum Blood | Dude | Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju | @SaiAbhyankkar | Paal Dabba |Keerthiswaran
snippet.description:
Presenting the Video song of 'Oorum Blood' from 'Dude', Written & Directed by Keerthiswaran featuring Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju, R.Sarath Kumar, Hridhu Haroon,Rohini, Aishwarya sharma, Dravid selvam & Others.

Allalley alla Dude

Othara Allalley alla Dude

Oorum Bloodu 
10000 Aura va kondu 
Achchadu
Nee ethanaiyo varuthangala paatha 
Athanaiyum worth nu thaan aakka

Dude‚Äôu unna minjinavan yaarum illa
Senjiru vachi
Just another person nu paathaa
ilichivan laa History ya kettaa

en Kaadhala kaamipen naa naa naa

Avan than Ennavanaa

Kalai Avan

Sari avan
Thavaravan

Avanthaan kaaranamaa

Kannan naa thottannaa poo malara
Ennenenna solla
Enna vella yaarum illa

naa vedikira 10000 wala hey!

snippet.title: Mirai Trailer Telugu | Teja Sajja | Manchu Manoj | Karthik Gattamneni | PMF | 12th Sept
snippet.description:
Presenting the most awaited #MiraiTrailer Telugu!!

#Mirai is an upcoming Indian action-adventure film starring  #TejaSajja, #ManchuManoj, Ritika Nayak & Others. Directed by Karthik Gattamneni. Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory. 

In Cinemas 12th September, 2025 Worldwide.

Cast: Super Hero Teja Sajja, Manoj Manchu, Ritika Nayak, Shriya Saran, Jayaram, Jagapathi Babu

snippet.title: Do You Wanna Partner - Official Trailer | Tamannaah Bhatia, Diana Penty | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Do You Wanna Partner Official Trailer
Starring Tamannaah Bhatia, Diana Penty, Jaaved Jaaferi, Nakuul Mehta, Neeraj Kabi, Shweta Tiwari, Sufi Motiwala, Rannjivay Singha, Lokesh Mittal, Indranil Sengupta, Ayesha Raza
Directed by Archit Kumar and Collin D'Cunha
Written by Nandini Gupta, Aarsh Vora and Mithun Gangopadhyay
Created by Mithun Gangopadhyay and Nishant Nayak
A Dharmatic Entertainment Production

Official Release Date September 12, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Best friends Shikha and Anahita turn entrepreneurs with an exciting craft beer brand, Jugaaro, to stand out in the crowded NCR beer market. However, they face gender discrimination every step of the way. To fight for an equal place in this male dominated sector, they decide to invent a fictitious male partner to help smooth their way. Invariably, things don‚Äôt go exactly as planned. What follows are their collective adventures & misadventures in trying to build a successful start-up amidst the current boom, as the bunch of misfits band together and become a family.

Tere dil pe haq mera hai
Tu sanam beshaq mera
Phir lakeerein hon ya na ho
Tu mera hai tu mera hai

Jo tu aag hai
Haan to phir mujhe
Jalne ka shauk hai
Jalne ka shauk hai
Marne se kahin
Jyada haan tujhe
Khone ka khauf hai
Khone ka khauf hai

Tu chahiye mujhe
Chahe kahe ise 
Mera junoon ya phir 
Tu zid meri


Tu hi armaan tu hi sach hai
Keh rahi deewaniyat hai
Main ye dil pe likh chuka hoon
Tu mera hai tu mera hai
Tere aage zindagi ki
Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai 
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera


Paane ki tujhko
Hasrat liye hi
Raaton ko main
Jagta hoon
Kyu jaane phir bhi
Dushaman teri do
Ankhon ko 
Main lagta hoon
Kahe na chahe tu mujhe
Karunga tujhe ishq main
Mujhe ye parwaah nahi 
Jo bhi ho mera anjaam har haal mein
Tu chahiye mujhe
Jo bhi saza mile 
Parwaah hai phir kise
Anjaam ki 
Tu hi armaan tu hi sach hai
Keh rahi deewaniyat hai
Main ye dil pe 
Likh chuka hu
Tu mera hai tu mera hai
Tere aage zindagi
Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera

snippet.title: Baahubali - The Epic Teaser | Prabhas, Rana Daggubati | SS Rajamouli | 31st October 2025
snippet.description:
Baahubali The Epic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli
Presented by: K. Raghavendra Rao B.A.
Producers: Shobu Yarlagadda & Prasad Devineni
Story: V. Vijayendra Prasad 
DOP: K.K. Senthil Kumar
Production Designer: Sabu Cyril
Music Composer: M.M. Keeravaani
VFX Supervision: V. Srinivas Mohan
Sound Design: P.M. Satheesh
Stunt Choreography: Peter Hein
Additional Stunts: King Solomon, Lee Whittakar, Kaloyan Vodenicharov

Dialogues:

snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil drops the much-awaited official trailer of Madharaasi, an action-packed emotional drama written and directed by A.R. Murugadoss. Starring Sivakarthikeyan in a bold, intense role alongside the talented Rukmini Vasanth, the trailer gives a powerful glimpse into a gripping narrative filled with high-stakes moments, strong character arcs, and impactful storytelling. Backed by a compelling background score from Anirudh Ravichander, Madharaasi promises to be a high-voltage entertainer that blends mass appeal with emotional depth.

With stunning visuals, hard-hitting dialogues, and a riveting plot, the Madharaasi trailer has already begun trending among fans of Tamil action movies, Sivakarthikeyan's latest films, and AR Murugadoss' direction. Whether you're here for the sharp screenplay, Anirudh‚Äôs electrifying music, or the powerful screen presence of the leads, this is one film that‚Äôs gearing up to be a Tamil cinema blockbuster in 2025. Don‚Äôt miss out‚Äîwatch the trailer now and be part of the growing excitement around #MadharaasiTrailer.

snippet.description:
Vengeance has a name. Watch the official trailer for #SISU: Road to Revenge - exclusively in movie theatres November 21.

Visit our site: http://sisuroadtorevenge.movie/

Follow us on social:
https://www.instagram.com/sisumovie
https://www.tiktok.com/@sisumovieofficial
https://www.facebook.com/sisumovieoffical/
https://twitter.com/sisumovie

Subscribe for more exclusive content: @sonypictures 

SISU: ROAD TO REVENGE is a wall-to-wall cinematic action event, a sequel to the original sleeper hit SISU. Returning to the house where his family was brutally murdered during the war, ‚Äúthe man who refuses to die‚Äù (Jorma Tommila) dismantles it, loads it on a truck, and is determined to rebuild it somewhere safe in their honor. When the Red Army commander who killed his family (Stephen Lang from Don‚Äôt Breathe) comes back hellbent on finishing the job, a relentless, eye-popping cross-country chase ensues - a fight to the death, full of clever, unbelievable action set pieces.

Directed by: Jalmari Helander

Written by: Jalmari Helander

Produced by: 
Mike Goodridge 
Petri Jokiranta

Executive Producers:
Gregory Ouanhon
Antonio Salas

Cast:
Jorma Tommila
Richard Brake
and Stephen Lang

snippet.title: Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
The survival action series "Alice in Borderland" became the most watched Japanese Netflix title by worldwide audiences.

Now, the "games" that took the world by storm begin once again.

In the previous season, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) and Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) cleared all of the games and returned to the real world. They have since gotten married and established a happy life together. Their memories of the borderland were erased, but they see glimpses of it in dreams and hallucinations. One day, Usagi, led by afterlife researcher Ryuji (#KentoKaku), suddenly vanishes. At the same time as Usagi's disappearance, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) hands Arisu the final card: the Joker.

The uncharted journey led by the mysterious Joker card is about to unfold...

Season 3 of the Netflix Series "Alice in Borderland" is set for worldwide release on Thursday, September 25, 2025, only on Netflix.

#AliceinBorderlandS3, #AliceinBorderland3, #Netflix

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81682895

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

When a morbid professor pulls Usagi back to Borderland, Arisu goes after her. But can he survive a new round of deadly games and escape the Joker's plans?

               ||Lyrics||

Main ta chetak leya palle addh ke,
Bebe ji de muhre haarhe kadd ke,
Suneya ae lancer ohne lai li
Ek time wali roti jahi chadd ke, Main ta chetak leya palle addh ke,
Bebe ji de muhre haarhe kadd ke,
Suneya ae lancer ohne lai li
Ek time wali roti jahi chadd ke
Rabba aida vadda faasla kyun saade vichkaar,
Oho daddy ji de cash utte kare jaave aish
Saada bapu zimidar kitho laye ke deve car,
Oh ta college di fees ohni bhardi
Saade aarth te jinne paise paye ne,
Khawaba waale mehal ussardi
Saade sadhran de ghar tahio dhahey ne,
Hun daso kive jurhu saade dil vaali taar,
Oho daddy ji de cash utte kare jaave aish
Saada bapu zimidar kitho laye ke deve car,
Oh ta vaddeya ch pali matt hor ae,
Tahi kar dena aapa ignore ae,
Bhola bhala mukh ohda jaapda
Par lagge mainu dil vich chor ae,
Shadd happy raikoti krna ni izhaar

snippet.title: Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha & Pooja Vidhanam | Ganesh Chaturthi Special | Vinayaka Chavithi Songs
snippet.description:
üôè Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha & Pooja Vidhanam ‚Äì A divine and sacred guide to performing Vinayaka Chavithi Vratham with proper rituals, mantras, and the traditional story of Lord Ganesha.

Narrated by : Tadala Srinivas, I. Muralidhara Sharma


Celebrate this Ganesh Chaturthi with devotion and learn the correct pooja procedure (Vidhanam) along with the auspicious Vinayaka Vratha Kadha in Telugu. This video is perfect for those who wish to observe the vratam at home with sincerity and faith.

Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha is a central part of the Vinayaka Vratham Telugu tradition, observed with deep devotion during VinayakaChavithi. On this auspicious day, devotees perform the Vinayaka Pooja Vidhanam Telugu, carefully following each of the Vinayaka Pooja Steps as outlined in the Ganesh Chaturthi Pooja Procedure.

The atmosphere is filled with devotion as families come together, guided by the Vinayaka Vratha Pooja Guide, to offer prayers and perform rituals. The celebration is further enhanced by spiritual music, including Vinayaka Chavithi Songs, Ganesh Chaturthi Special Songs, and uplifting Lord Ganesha Devotional Songs.

Songs like Vinayaka Aarti Telugu, Ganesh Bhakti Songs Telugu, and the latest Vinayaka Chavithi 2025 Telugu Songs add a divine rhythm to the puja. This GaneshChaturthiSpecial becomes even more meaningful when observed with heartfelt devotion, traditional GaneshChaturthiPooja, and the blessings of Lord Ganesha.

üåø Highlights:
‚úî Complete Vinayaka Chavithi Pooja Vidhanam
‚úî Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha in Telugu
‚úî Ideal for Ganesh Chaturthi festival celebrations

‚ú® Chant, pray, and invite Lord Vinayaka‚Äôs blessings for prosperity, wisdom, and happiness.
